{"tid":384863,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(另一版本MV發佈)(陳飛機主唱)  2017阿仙奴新會歌《絕》(記於晏菲路慘劇後)","createTime":"2017-09-02T16:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T04:55:57.000Z","uid":34934,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"321712ad74f93ba97c8276e7cbc8159642925e4b","tid":384863,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:28:56.000Z","msg":"link在此 : <a href=\"https://youtu.be/l8XTw4tZI9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fl8XTw4tZI9c&d=ZoqK%2FXN3%2BWtxG0VrodnihROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c00e8b7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/l8XTw4tZI9c</a><br />\n<br />\n我知Subway 巴早前已經整咗，只係身為阿迷想剪另外一條，無任何冒犯嘅意思。另外小弟第一次整，多多見諒。<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 睇到最後，最後我擺咗幾張心up嘅相。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴新會歌《絕》<br />\n主唱:陳飛機<br />\n作曲:陳輝陽<br />\n原詞:黃偉文<br />\n新詞:芥子納須彌（暗紅）<br />\nMV:拿樸迪<br />\n<br />\n原Post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/382217/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/382217/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nMp3版: <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/aeroplanewing/zqlznhnpz5c0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Faeroplanewing%2Fzqlznhnpz5c0&d=ZoqK%2FXN3%2BWtxG0VrodnihROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1e6aaa40\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/aeroplanewing/zqlznhnpz5c0</a><br />\n<br />\n宏願滯留在歐霸　無謂惹憐憫丟架<br />\n我山已竊笑如麻　奧燒眼角有淚花<br />\n連敗後防亦風化　錯擺邊衛陣容吧<br />\n任你闖　無形的罅　編寫這結局正落霞<br />\n<br />\n購兵全局失敗　販賣更瀟灑<br />\n轉會求利馬　卻沒營利予身價<br />\n<br />\n梅菲眼望望　拿卡眼望望<br />\n而基奧特要面臨完場才被釋放<br />\n蒙維漸心慌　回傳任宰割<br />\n從此教授與列文徬徨　盡數哭喪<br />\n<br />\n藍斯已滴汗　薩卡會亂撞<br />\n留中線互望利城球員傳射幾趟<br />\n難再協防　翼衛更荒唐<br />\n他朝要滑跪將東家重創<br />\n<br />\n客軍臨晏菲路　見叛將影子<br />\n已轉投利市　與近年狀況相似<br />\n<br />\n梅菲眼望望　拿卡眼望望<br />\n而基奧特要面臨完場才被釋放<br />\n蒙維漸心慌　回傳任宰割<br />\n從此教授與列文徬徨　盡數哭喪<br />\n<br />\n藍斯已滴汗　薩卡會亂撞<br />\n留中線互望利城球員傳射幾趟<br />\n難再協防　翼衛更荒唐<br />\n他朝要滑跪將東家重創<br />\n<br />\n球會裡動盪　無爭勝慾望<br />\n如張伯倦怠臉容神情純屬虛妄<br />\n球員賣清光　球迷亦羞看<br />\n雲加永續至下游沉淪地老天荒<br />\n<br />\n還不滿現狀　浩鼎更絕望<br />\n如高塔屹立任由文尼隨便奔放<br />\n頹廢至極　耗盡了鋒芒<br />\n將爭四夢幻都風光殮葬<br />\n<br />\n聞道未來是牽強 習慣安逸或愚戇<br />\n讓眾槍 提前釋放<br />\n誰不會續約 或許應該要放<br />\n<br />\n雲格這樣 才盡似江郎<br />\n轉會費賺盡的商家答案"},{"pid":"f4a0629ff3a8be9e65ead9e8a08373e0c1de5cf9","tid":384863,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3766199a5b21407456d74a413cf83ccbf1593547","tid":384863,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"俾人BAM咗，盡快 reupload"},{"pid":"e07274439a4a39a8c4edc68d267c654a3d2cba81","tid":384863,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:30:46.000Z","msg":"秒bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e1bd4f0a5751b5b344c12858e373d9703c2af0","tid":384863,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>秒bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b5e30c1f4f32f80c5e823ba2a35962ae325ee5","tid":384863,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:33:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3d1040a94a2fc491d01fbecdc24c4509a005237","tid":384863,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45dc7e03f64457f1918073e20c801e3adb6e581f","tid":384863,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Up上youku啦，大家都係中國人都睇到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n六日子好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1ede3628ea6e19d338dcec5c3925b8074edf4f","tid":384